events.name: SPC Summer 2025 Demo Faire
events.description: ​Curious what the brilliant minds of SPC are up to?​​​​Join us for a showcase of the latest demos from SPC alumni and members.These are no slideshows—live demos only!​​​Demos will be in person at SPC-SF from 1:30-4:30pm PT. After demos wrap we will host an open house until 6pm PT so you can meet the presenters and mix with SPC members. We hope you'll join us in person!​​​Schedule​​​1:00pm PT - Doors open at SPC-SF​​​1:30pm PT - Demos start​​​4:30pm PT - Demos end, open house starts​​​6:00pm PT - Open house ends​​​About South Park Commons​​​SPC is ahome for the most talented technologistsfiguring out what's next—a community designed to turn the chaos of possibility into the clarity of conviction. Whether you're exploring startup ideas, refining your thinking on a new product, or looking to dive into a new domain, we're here to help you get from -1 to 0.
